[@Honeybadga](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64977-honeybadga/) - you need to change [GameData/ContractConfigurator/science/DMagicOrbitalScience.cfg](https://github.com/jrossignol/ContractConfigurator/blob/master/GameData/ContractConfigurator/science/DMagicOrbitalScience.cfg).  The module manager config would look something like this:

    @CC_EXPERIMENT_DEFINITIONS[DMagicOrbitalScience]
    {
        @EXPERIMENT[dmbathymetryscan]
        {
            ignored = true
        }
    }

And it's always the ice caps because the RNG is programmed to be evil. ![:0.0:](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif ":0.0:")
